ate government support many faculty members' research programs. These grants often include support for graduate students seeking Ph.D. or master degrees. Algebra Doug Brozovic Charles Conley (Representations of Lie Algebras) Matt Douglass (Representation Theory of Groups of Lie Type and Related Topics) Joseph Kung Anne Shepler Applied Mathematics, Optimization and Numerical Analysis Rajeev Azad (Mathematical Biology) Robert Kallman J. Jianguo Liu John Quintanilla Combinatorics Joseph Kung Anne Shepler Neal Brand (Graph Theory) Matt Douglass (Combinatorics of Coxeter Groups, Kazhdan-Lusztig Theory) Differential Equations Joe Iaia Dynamical Systems Lior Fishman Su Gao Steve Jackson Mariusz Urbański Logic and Foundations Su Gao Steve Jackson John Krueger Functional Analysis Robert Kallman Bunyamin Sari Geometry and Topology Nicolae Anghel (Spin Geometry) Neal Brand (Branched Coverings) Matt Douglass (Intersection (Co)-homology, Equivariant K-theory) Mariusz Urbański Number Theory William Cherry Lior Fishman Olav Richter (Automorphic Forms) Mariusz Urbański Probability and Statistics Pieter Allaart (Optimal stopping and stochastic processes) John Quintanilla Kai-Sheng Song Real and Complex Analysis Pieter Allaart (Fractal Analysis) Nicolae Anghel (Geometric Analysis) William Cherry Robert Kallman Mariusz Urbański Thinking about UNT? It's easy to apply online. Join us and discover why we're the choice of over 37,000 students. Apply now Contact Us (940) 565-2155 mathchair@unt.edu Visit Us General Academic Building 435 Send Us Mail 1155 Union Circle #311430 Denton, Texas 76203-5017 Fax: (940) 565-4805 Follow Us FacebookTwitter College of Science View departments Get advising University of North Texas Explore our degrees Take a tour Get financial aid Apply online Find a person Register for classes Follow UNT on social media Disclaimer AA/EOE/ADA Privacy Statement Electronic Accessibility State of Texas Online Emergency Preparedness THECB Online Resume System Student Consume